'''Aṛekka''' neɣ '''Aṛak''' ([[Assaɣ ussnan]]: '''Vulpes rueppellii''') d yiwet n [[Talmest|telmest]] n [[abareɣ|iburaɣ]] yeṭṭafaren [[tawacult (tasnudert)|tawacult]] n [[taydiyyin]], yettidir deg [[Tafriqt n Ugafa|Tefrikt n ugafa]] d [[asamar alemmas|usamar alemmas]]. Talmest-a [[asirem n tudert|tettidir]] gar n 6 ar 7 n iseggasen.

== Aglam ==
Teɣzi n tfekka n uṛekka gar n 40 ar 50 cm. Yettazen 1,7 kg ma d tiddi-ynes ar tuyat 25 cm ɣef wanecta aṛekka iga d [[aɣersiw]] meẓẓiyen yakk deg twacult-is "[[taydiyyin]]", Aṛekka meẓẓiy uma ɣef [[arraɣ|warraɣ]] maca meqqer s imik (cwiya) ɣef [[aɣecter|uɣecter]]

== Tudert d umyaraw ==
Iṛekka ttidiren d tayuga neɣ d tagrawt deg kra n tama meẓẓiyen, ma d addaden n [[amercel|umercel-nsen]] ar tura ur ttwassnen  mya amdan-nsen deg uzɣar (lexla) ur tettwassen ara ɣef wanect-a [[Umuɣ azeggaɣ n IUCN|Umuɣ azeggaɣ n telmas yettwaggzen]] ur t-ittessismil ara deg kra n [[Addad n taggaẓt|waddad abadu]] acku ulac aṭas n isalan fell-as maca llan kra [[asnudran|isnudranen]] id yeqqaren d akken aṛekka d [[talmest ur tettwaggez]]

